Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,30,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:41.53,Default,,0,0,30,,Please call me a High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that period
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:48.46,Default,,0,0,30,,When it gets so hard to be honest with people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:57.26,Default,,0,0,30,,I just want to know what's in his heart, \Nwhen he goes away, I want him to turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:24:00.13,Default,,0,0,30,,to give me a loving glance one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:05.64,Default,,0,0,30,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:10.60,Default,,0,0,30,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:16.78,Default,,0,0,30,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
