Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Taishou Era, an era of Romanticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that quiet girl is none other than Hanamura Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a seventeen-year-old High Collar Lady.{dc: "well she was just seventeen, and you know what i mean"}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But a single bamboo sword is all she needs \Nto transform into a full-blown tomboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,People are sometimes brought together in strange and interesting ways...{縁は異なもの味なもの - Japanese proverb, roughly translates to "bonds are a strange and interesting thing" - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the case for Benio,{dc: little text flavor}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as fate had her run into a \Nprincely Second Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She challenged him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to test his reflexes,{I don't really understand what he's saying. I went with the Italian version.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,only to discover that she had been betrothed to him by her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde! Ten points!{dc: check this line and the one before it for consistency with episode 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle twinkle little star,\Nhow I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're finally awake, Young Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that said a warrior should always be vigilant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I've never lost to anyone before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it gets me all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Howdy, I'm Boozy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me, I'm just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She heated up nicely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you? \NCan't you see I've got a lot on my mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that guy's going to be my fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fiancé? My future husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&HEEEFFE&\pos(750,450)\bord0\blur1\fs60.333}Episode 2\N{\fs140}Eloping
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's funny \Nwhen you joke around like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so stop messing around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is definitely not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin Shinobu is your \Nhusband-to-be, and that's final.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, now is not the time to faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father, this is so out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For ages, the Hanamura dynasty was a vassal family in service of the Tokugawa Shogunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,while the Ijuuin dynasty was always a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, your grandfather and Ijuuin's grandmother, who met each other by chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,fell in love with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, on the night before the Meiji Restoration began,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they were forced to break off their relationship due to the end of the Shogunate.{I added a bit of context to it  - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, before they parted ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they swore that someday, \Nonce the world became a better place,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that their two families would become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The rapid flow of water \Nmay get split in two by a stepping stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will eventually become one again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However, despite that, their descendants were male,{dc: is this descendant singular or descendants plural?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so they decided to wait until \Ntheir grandchildren were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words, I'm the chosen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this was a promise that long predated your births.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got to be kidding me! \NThere's no way I'm going to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't I get a say in this? \NThat promise has long since expired,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the deal is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And with a guy like him, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to accept that this is an\Neverlasting promise between the families.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And to break a promise \Nis to discard your humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We are both bound by this military oath:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Warriors! Let faithfulness be your creed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that guy isn't a warrior. He's a coward \Nwho hits people when they're not looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those military oaths also say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"First and foremost, \Netiquette shall be followed."{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio! Don't object to your father's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be holding an informal wedding in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to Ijuuin's house will help you learn some manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, is the bath ready?{dc: check this for consistency with whatever we called her in ep 1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, \Nthis is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad this happened. \NI've always treated Benio like a child...{dc: changed}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I hadn't done something, she would've gotten more and more tomboyish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, her fiancé is from a good, \Nnoble family, so she'll learn a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...even though it might be difficult at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"That is the question."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"To be or not to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the question,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,remember that one well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a line from a work by William Shakespeare, \Na famous English playwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura Benio, interpret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpret this line: "To be or not to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the question!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It means the author is asking himself whether something is there or not.{/alternative: There is. There is not. That is a question.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing, Benio? Read this!}Where are you at, Benio?! Read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:38.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2896AB&\3c&H0E3A4D&}Cheatsheet - English{トラの巻 - colloqual for cheatsheet in Japanese, literally "Tiger's book" - pere}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that suffering in life is better than dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that is his dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just reading right off the cheatsheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, should I keep reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Get out of this class!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Saved by the bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey, hey, Benio, what's wrong with you?}Hey, Benio, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Isn't English your best subject?}I thought English was your strong suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in a daze all morning long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.80,Top,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to tell the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been betrothed to \Nsomeone I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Betrothed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{You, Benio?}You, of all people, Benio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a real man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you, the dunce, would be the first to get engaged!{dc: cut "usual", it sounded weird}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Benio, you animal!}Benio, you sly dog, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People sure have strange tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's true!}No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme your man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he's handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get married yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have interests, \Nhopes and dreams too, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's easy for you guys to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She shouldn't be forced to marry a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are well within your rights to reject this old-fashioned marriage custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki, you're the only one who understands me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're too picky, you might end up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes even I worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Living your whole life alone is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, cheer up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, didn't you say that this man is a noble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from a noble family too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Life in a noble family is hard, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard? How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, "Omawari," "Akaka,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Iriiri,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Okabe," "Misomiso," "Tsukutsuku," "Harihari," "Surusuru."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it short,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Omawari" stands for vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Akaka" are azuki beans.{/azuki beans}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Iriiri" are soybeans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Okabe" means tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, "Misomiso" is miso dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Harihari" stands for dried melon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tsukutsuku."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Surusuru."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these are words nobles use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't speak Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is a rather different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A world without Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I'd hate a place like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Tamaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{I get it, I get it, Tenmaru.}Okay, I hear you, Tenmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chimaru, good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, is Grandmother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is currently on the terrace in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Tenmaru, Chimaru, we'll play later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back home, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. \NI'm sure you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, I got to meet \NLady Hanamura yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Tell me, Shinobu, how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of lady was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed to be full of spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say it went well.{dc: i struggled with the good impression thing for a bit, ended up cutting it}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you would be willing to marry that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything to make you happy, Grandmother.{not literal but sounds the best in this case - Alucard}{dc: isn't he saying something like "if that's what you want, grandmother?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The rapid flow of water
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,may get split in two by a stepping stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will eventually become one again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you, as my grandson, have granted one of my lifetime wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much, Shinobu.}I can't thank you enough, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is today's share of letters for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are from women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, I hear your engagement came through, \Nso why don't you try to discourage them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{How can I blame them, though.}Can you blame them, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Young Master is so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I might send him a love letter, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.13,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1A160E&\bord0\blur1\pos(192,96)\fade(0,200)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Shinobu!{dc: do we need to include the -san somehow?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my way back from piano class,\N so I thought I'd drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see, I'd love to hear you play sometime.}Really? I'd love to hear you play sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You always get so many love letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it pales in comparison \Nto the number you must receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, you charmer!}My, always the charmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Today, a friend of mine got betrothed.}A friend of mine got betrothed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, her fiancé is a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so he's like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I'll get lucky, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but shouldn't it be easy for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with all the proposals you get every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki is too different from my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't possibly be friends with {\i1}her{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:32.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H50443F&\3c&HCAC6B9&\move(773,772,773,-50,1000,3798)}Flower Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These safflowers are a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they'd suit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Uh?}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you send some flowers to this address?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sure thing! Oh, getting a gift for your girlfriend?}Sure thing! Sending a gift to your girlfriend, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{My!}The nerve...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{dc: liberal tl}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{but if you act this carelessly, your reputation will certainly be damaged!}but your reputation is sure to be damaged\N if you keep acting so carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never acknowledged my feelings at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,even back when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's spring, and yet it's still so cold.}My goodness, is it cold for spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Grilled chicken, your favorite!}It's your favorite, chicken dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's always been her favorite, but now she won't even open the door.}Even her favorites won't get her \Nto open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{A hunger strike...}So it's a hunger strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{Then she really must be serious.}She must be really serious then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But she'll eventually get sick \Nif she keeps on going like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we shouldn't be so hasty, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls who are betrothed usually go through some self-reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.19,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H131679&\3c&H476E9C&}Here Comes the High Collar Lady{dc: breaking the fourth wall i see}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,King, King, Ki—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not funny anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I do, I still can't cheer up.{dc: kind of liberal?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even feel like practicing fencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought it was quiet. It's snowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{You fool, what are you standing there for?}Why are you standing\N out here in the snow like a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't help it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get near the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How long were you standing outside like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, it's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You being betrothed... betrothed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,always liked you, ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But my social status is lower than yours, and I'm a year younger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I've never told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go against my father's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, according to what he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that second lieutenant seems to be a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But to make such a decision, all of a sudden, when there was so much I wanted to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ranmaru, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give up everything to be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd even give up kabuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Am I not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that.\N I {\i1}do{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a more brotherly way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's okay, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet tonight, I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{To tell me something like that, \Nhe went all this way through the snow.}He stood in the snow \Nall this time to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this warm feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this all happening so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ranmaru {\i1}is{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can't just ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But to run away with him?\N That's a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Something drastic like eloping\N doesn't sound like the smart thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare said:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is it better to suffer in life than to die? \NThat is the question."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ijuuin sent some flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These are safflowers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He even attached a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's not a color
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very fond of..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a color I'm very fond of, but, for some reason,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I picked out these safflowers for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's not a color I'm very fond of,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,so, what he's saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he doesn't have deep feelings about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,he still decided to send these safflowers with some kind of intention, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Safflowers, typically used as a dye...{Here she makes a pun with 紅花 (紅 meaning red/crimson and 花(flower) having the same reading as 鼻(nose)), so I had to change it in some way for it to make sense / she also makes a joke with Benio, her name, and Benibana - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers meant for dyeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So he wanted to dye my nose red?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that no-good—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he'd be this mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never liked him, but now I'm completely done with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm running away, no matter what! \NYou think I'd marry him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No one dares make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ranmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{Goodbye Dad,}This is goodbye! To my dad, {home, friends,}my home, my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{and fiancé, I'll be making my own way from now on!}and to my fiancé! From now on,\N I'll be going down my own path!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, walking at a fast pace alongside Ranmaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,High Collar Benio is determined to start anew.
